  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A Phase 2 study to evaluate the safety and efficacy of two different once daily doses VX-135
      in combination with ribavirin in treatment-na誰ve subjects with chronic hepatitis C
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
